const about_app_text="Welcome to Adop Box, your go-to app for finding your new furry companion. Our app was designed with the goal of making pet adoption easy and accessible for everyone.\n\nWith Adop Box, you can browse through thousands of pets from reputable adoption agencies and shelters in your area. Our app features a simple and user-friendly interface that allows you to filter your search results by breed, age, and location, making it easy to find the perfect pet that fits your lifestyle.\n\nWe understand that adopting a pet is a big decision, which is why we provide detailed information about each pet, including their personality traits, medical history, and temperament. We also offer tips and advice on how to prepare for your new pet's arrival and how to properly care for them.\n\nAt Adop Box, we are committed to promoting responsible pet ownership and improving the lives of pets in need. Our app makes it easy to connect with reputable adoption agencies and shelters that are dedicated to finding loving homes for their pets. We also donate a portion of our proceeds to animal welfare organizations to support their efforts in helping animals in need.\n\nThank you for choosing Adop Box as your pet adoption app. We hope that our app helps you find your perfect furry companion and brings joy to your life for years to come.";

const privacy_text="Thank you for choosing to use our pet adoption app. At our company, we take privacy and the security of your personal information very seriously. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the information you provide to us through our pet adoption app.\n\nInformation We Collect: We may collect personal information from you when you use our pet adoption app. This information may include your name, email address, phone number, location, and other personal information necessary to help you find and adopt a pet through our app. We may also collect information about the type of pet you are interested in adopting, your lifestyle, and preferences.\n\nHow We Use Your Information: We use the personal information we collect from you to help you find and adopt a pet through our app. We may also use your information to communicate with you about your pet adoption search, to provide you with updates about our app, and to respond to your inquiries or requests for information. We may also use your information to improve our app and to personalize your experience.\n\nWe may share your personal information with third-party service providers who assist us in providing our pet adoption app. We may also share your information with pet adoption agencies or organizations to help you find a pet to adopt. We will not sell, rent, or disclose your personal information to any third party without your consent, except as required by law.\n\nHow We Protect Your Information: We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, or alteration. We use secure servers, firewalls, and other security technologies to protect your information. However, no security measures are 100% foolproof, and we cannot guarantee the security of your information.\n\nYour Choices: You can choose not to provide us with certain personal information, but this may limit your ability to use our pet adoption app. You may also have the option to opt-out of certain communications from us. You can contact us to update or correct your personal information or to request that we delete your personal information.\n\nChildren's Privacy: Our pet adoption app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If you are under the age of 13, please do not use our app or provide us with any personal information.\n\nChanges to Our Privacy Policy: We may update our privacy policy from time to time. If we make material changes to our privacy policy, we will notify you by email or by posting a notice on our app. We encourage you to review our privacy policy periodically to stay informed about how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.\n\nContact Us: If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at [insert contact information].\n\nEffective Date: 7 Apr 2023";